column2: SELECT top # G.objid as HostGal_OBJID, GN.distance as NN1 FROM Galaxy as G JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(ra,dec, #) AS GN ON G.objID = GN.objID WHERE ra IN (SELECT r.BOSS_HEADS_RA FROM MyDB.BOSS_HEADS_RA as r )    AND dec IN (SELECT d.BOSS_HEADS_DEC FROM MyDB.BOSS_HEADS_DEC as d) ORDER BY distance OFFSET # ROWS /*Skip first # rows*/   FETCH NEXT # ROWS ONLY
